{"tid":1032040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"FT: 金管局將於未來數周發放六張虛擬銀行牌照 包括騰訊，小米，渣打，中信，香港電訊","createTime":"2019-02-22T05:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T06:00:28.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"292c166a7f39d0f2b71dc08f278018ed7eddabad","tid":1032040,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T05:46:16.000Z","msg":"報道指本港將於未來數周發放六張虛擬銀行牌照<br />\n<br />\n        英國《金融時報》報道, 本港將於未來幾個星期內, 發出6張虛擬銀行牌照, 預計獲批牌照的運營商, 包括騰訊(00700)旗下的支付業務財付通, 小米(01810)螞蟻金服, 渣打(02888), 香港電訊(06823), 以及眾安在線(06060)和其合作伙伴中信銀行(00998). 早前有報道指, 騰訊等8家公司虛擬銀行牌照申請入圍下輪甄選.<br />\n        本港有超過50家公司有意經營虛擬銀行, 金管局副總裁阮國恒在上月底表示, 爭取在今年首季就虛擬銀行發牌, 未來亦將加強虛擬銀行科技監管. <br />\n<br />\n阮國恒指, 科技是虛擬銀行唯一的服務渠道, 將更看重科技風險管理, 又指早前收到的申請較預期多, 目前正處理經篩選後的個案, 但當中牽涉大量審批工作, 需要更多時間處理.<br />\n        <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/default.aspx?NewsId=20190222111529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2FNews%2Fdefault.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20190222111529&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLQDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=21151d21\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/default.aspx?NewsId=20190222111529</a><br />\n<br />\n啱啱講完換總裁就⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩人接任無懸念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc884115ac4585f3fd0c11bd1bfe49da9ddc835","tid":1032040,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T05:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d474d9d46563e49869ce802556e8c19d2c4f2882","tid":1032040,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T06:00:28.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<br />\n全面入侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}